    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? You\u2019ve found it! This car is an absolute gem and has been pampered like a member of the family. It\u2019s in pristine shape, inside and out\u2014honestly, you\u2019d be hard-pressed to find a single flaw. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. I\u2019ve taken so much pride in keeping it in top-notch condition, and I know you're going to love it. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come see this beauty in person!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
