    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six. This specimen exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders and a flawlessly calibrated double VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission delivering tactile engagement through a refreshed short-throw linkage. Performance is optimized via the factory M Variable Differential Lock and a chassis that has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement with TMS plates. The suspension geometry remains true, riding on original bushings that show zero signs of fatigue. The Carbon Black Metallic finish retains its factory depth, free of orange peel or swirling, while the interior preserves its Nappa leather integrity without bolster wear. A mechanically transparent, turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
