    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior features the original factory paint with a deep, glass-like finish, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating\u2014there are absolutely no swirl marks, dings, or stone chips to be found. Step inside to an interior that remains indistinguishable from new; the premium leather seats are supple with zero bolster wear, and the cabin retains its original scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced driver assistance features, functions perfectly. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history exclusively performed at authorized dealerships. It has never seen rain or snow, and the undercarriage is as clean as the body. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle.",
